story.text: Redux of my first hearing today. Driving to GF and looking forward to impressing Ted (hopefully).

Anna is gone. Kamila will be here shortly. I love them both very much - different as they are. One is the queen of Video, the other of Audio. A true team to build an empire if I ever could dream of one.
